-- Areva Set to Announce $3 Billion of Chinese Contracts, Les Echos Reports
-- B y   V i c t o r i a   R i c h a r d s
-- 2010-11-02T00:19:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/areva-set-to-announce-3-billion-of-chinese-contracts-les-echos-reports.html
Areva SA is set to announce a
contract worth $3 billion for the delivery of uranium to China
Guangdong Nuclear Power Corp., Les Echos reported, without
saying where it got the information from.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Richards at 
